title: Free Vimager 5.1.0 Portable
description:
Free Vimager 5.1.0 Portable



Just download and copy or put the exe file in a folder of your choice then 

use it!  It is free to use!  It is portable - NO install whatsoever!




Publisher	Contaware 
Price	Free
Version	5.1.0  
Last updated	Sep 20, 2016
File Size	4.08 Mb	
Requirements	None



Portable Image Viewer
FreeVimager is a portable image viewer and editor that offers high quality 

image viewing along with several handy image editing features such as red-eye 

removal, image cropping, color and brightness adjustments, image borders and 

image resizing. The program also includes a slideshow viewing mode with 

transition effects that can play all images in the current folder.
Other features include metadata display and editing (EXIF, IPTC, XMP, ICC), 

click-zooming, print preview, emailing of (optimized) images, Geotag look-up 

and more. FreeVimager can also be used to convert images to PDF format and to 

scan documents and save them as PDF files.

Reality Ascent by Dragan Glavasic
